                The best Hostel in town for lone travellers where everything is near you
                The best Hostel in town for lone travellers where everything is near you
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col text-center">
            <a href="/booking">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</button>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
<div class="row my-footer">
    <div class="col">
        Left
    </div>
